<i>- This is Bob's birthday, July 22nd, 1992.</i>
- Are you ready?

1169
01:18:18,262 --> 01:18:20,112
Are you ready for the pyrotechnics?

1170
01:18:20,112 --> 01:18:21,573
<i>- Yeah! </i>

