<i>George Marshall,</i>
en mijn geliefde broer, Dennis Jay.

1174
01:18:47,244 --> 01:18:53,232
<i>- Robert R. Hackett,</i>
Philip Gregory Alliston.

1175
01:18:55,290 --> 01:18:59,369
<i>Teri Ronan.</i>
- Michael Benetton.

1176
01:18:59,369 --> 01:19:02,519


1177
01:19:02,970 --> 01:19:06,847
<i>- Tina Chao.</i>
Perry Ellis.

1178
01:19:07,702 --> 01:19:10,876
<i>Freddie Mercury.</i>
Peter Allen.

1179
01:19:12,639 --> 01:19:19,051
<i>En aan de duizenden anderen </i>
die in stilte hebben geleden.

1180
